posting_body: ['Welcome to Chorus', "Chorus is prominently and conveniently located at the cross point of SF's most dynamic neighborhoods.", 'The private residences are complete with the latest technology and top-of-the-line appliances.', 'Outside the home, Chorus residents enjoy access to a unique collection of amenities including a rooftop pool, outdoor American Ninja Warrior course, solarium, speakeasy and lobby cocktail bar.', 'The community is expertly maintained 24 hours a day by a dedicated team with attention to every detail.', 'Join the Chorus family today!', 'Amenities Include:', 'Bike Storage & Repair', 'Speakeasy gaming lounge with skee ball, foosball and arcade favorites', 'Valet parking', 'Dog run, grooming station and pet wash', 'Adjacent Chorus Hall 227-seat performing arts venue', 'Co-working space with private conference rooms', 'Skybox lounge', 'Backyard terrace with pizza oven', 'Attended arrival desk', 'Public art plaza', 'Rooftop solarium with floating fireplace, private dining kitchen and skyline views', 'Indoor/outdoor fitness lab with functional training equipment and 10 rotating classes per week', 'Call:', 'show contact info', 'For more information, visit us at: <URL>', '*Pricing and availability are subject to change daily.', 'Photos may not be of the exact advertised unit.', 'Please contact us today for the most up to date information!']
